 </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uaurianne.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aurianne</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(11/26/01 5:38:15 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://rkroll.magma.ca/aurie/pics/avatar5.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Staff of the Wheel</span><hr size=1> I feel your pain...<br>
